{"tid":1770463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來鄧曱甴上北京係要傾點將香港人送中","createTime":"2019-12-05T09:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:59:32.000Z","uid":19527,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd97e5b41b4e699c35720bfa7e016970331dc417","tid":1770463,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"上月就任的警務處處長鄧炳強明日前赴北京，進行禮節性拜訪。<br />\n<br />\n訪京期間，鄧炳強將到公安部及港澳辦，與北京相關官員會面，介紹香港的治安情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">並就跨境罪案及警務合作方面進行交流。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務處副處長蕭澤頤將陪同訪京，並於周日返港。<br />\n<br />\n同埋講到警務合作，即刻諗起呢份<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pj.gov.mo/Web//u/cms/www/201903/041620179xxn.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pj.gov.mo%2FWeb%2F%2Fu%2Fcms%2Fwww%2F201903%2F041620179xxn.pdf&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=4764a219\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pj.gov.mo/Web//u/cms/www/201903/041620179xxn.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n結論就係呢隻鄧曱甴好想幫中共清洗哂你班香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae56d93ba176b2f1aa85d129c82082681680ead","tid":1770463,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNWdf8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNWdf8E.jpg&h=8384cbd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"390366cf80997636b10257907b81fee4ceaf3154","tid":1770463,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:40:02.000Z","msg":"咁同重新推返送中條例有乜分別<br />\n班狗覺得你犯法就可以直接拉鳩你<br />\n而班狗又會聽上頭中共支笛, 唔止係對付示威者喎, 一得閒就順便搞鳩埋d商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a47fc2f6b9a57bbab9d48b04063fd4eefbbad9","tid":1770463,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislik